4 NEW SECTION. Section 7. Credentials. After a commissioner's executed oath is filed with the
5 secretary of state as required in [section 6], the clerk of the house of representatives shall provide to the
6 commissioner an official copy of the executed oath and the commissioning resolution, which together serve as
7 the commissioner's credentials.
